  "detailed_description": "House of God is a chaotic Rogue-Lite shooter, taking place on a randomly generated train with a heavy focus on item synergies. Following Jack as they pull the trigger, hold it down, and run headlong towards the conductor to save their dead loved one.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKey features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Randomly generated train <br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 50+ unique items (majority capable of synergizing)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 4 Bosses<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 4 unique areas with unique enemy additions<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 80 handcrafted rooms",
